# Project Context

This project uses a `_context/` knowledge base. When working on SubsTrack:

1. Read `_context/context.md` for a quick project overview
2. Deeper context in `_context/architecture.md`, `_context/stack.md`, `_context/conventions.md`, `_context/integrations.md`
3. After completing a task, update relevant `_context/` files if you discovered something new

Key documentation:
- `AGENTS.md` — directory map, key files, common tasks
- `docs/PLAN.md` — full architecture and feature roadmap
- `docs/data-models.md` — Mongoose schema docs
- `docs/api-design.md` — API reference
